Diagram 1 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Capturing the cutting stone with 1, is correct and white's only response.
\par
\par It allows black to take profit with 2 and 4 but white gets very good shape after capturing with 3.
\par
\par White then occupies a good point with 5 and ruins black's plan to close in white's group here. This is not a desirable result for black.
\par }
